| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2942 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ebcb5e7c-93e0-5fb3-ad3b-68726216a53b"
